Options to include in a config for TS:

Preferred Resolution
Enable/Disable Audio
Manually set OpenGL library
Video Settings:
	VSync
	Allow HW Surfaces
	Enable Asynchronous Blits
	Enable DoubleBuffering

Things to check for auto-configuration:
	Number of CPU cores:
		>1:
			Enable AsyncBlit
		>2:
			Enable Audio Threading
	Graphics Cards:
		Share System Memory:
			Disable HW Surfaces
			Disable Async Blits
		Intel or other integrated graphics:
			Disable Double Buffering
